{"tid":1941603,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"連詩雅：見戴手帶人士違規必舉報","createTime":"2020-03-24T13:36:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-28T22:56:44.000Z","uid":242050,"like":10,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"4af0853d9021cf0fd26da8fa4722ab93967eaed5","tid":1941603,"uid":242050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T13:36:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XFXjOzQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXFXjOzQ.png&h=3aa5236b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vf83vOc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVf83vOc.png&h=5e49cad8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n連B<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b93c37eb5baff321b0245dba8af9aafa2e466c94","tid":1941603,"uid":48124,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T02:21:36.000Z","msg":"有無留意到呢幾日有好多傳媒都好似夾埋咁大做「帶着手帶離家出走自私撚」既故仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後林鄭配合聲淚俱下，每次記者會都喺度屌鳩呢啲人自私<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n根本上就係想將大家將個怒氣spin落捉鬼捉自私撚，慢慢淡化林鄭一開始唔封關嘅事，同時支持政府加大監控<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />乘機推行d監控嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n由二月中至三月頭，由支那陸路入境嘅人一直冇需要帶任何手帶，淨係間中喺電話分享location就當隔離左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢啲嘢又冇人講<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n下次見到有「哇有個手帶人又去XXX食嘢」呢一類post，嘗試下唔好講「 仆你個街又係呢啲自私撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n<br />\n試吓講「呢啲自私撚固然唔應該出街，但最仆街嘅都係林鄭一開始唔支那封關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />害死全香港人」"},{"pid":"cb4cd3d1196ea3ac093a5e50831ef0c0fb6505c7","tid":1941603,"uid":227660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T10:42:45.000Z","msg":"連屎眼"},{"pid":"319b29278bfed60ab7efea8fda25ff8d7e4918fa","tid":1941603,"uid":15660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T12:38:23.000Z","msg":"正氣"},{"pid":"8b0634eeb123921ee8a2da433b4e52219666f6ad","tid":1941603,"uid":186431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T12:40:37.000Z","msg":"3條女都想屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a021b32a18489c61d3d869573bf1223b6771c32","tid":1941603,"uid":123053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T12:51:30.000Z","msg":"好想狂奶佢對腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09e54f47489ee56272477b3ec2380c3bf111dbfb","tid":1941603,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T12:56:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ScnPX8a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FScnPX8a.png&h=5ac68271&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5gb9dGv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5gb9dGv.png&h=eb589fc4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SmfepOb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSmfepOb.png&h=b9d6f5ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9V9ZAUS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9V9ZAUS.png&h=0549fa29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rbFRr1y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrbFRr1y.png&h=cae8d941&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tA5YRte.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtA5YRte.png&h=bc270070&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QYyPdGA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2